{"tid":826182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真正第一滴血]【山竹災後】西貢發現男屍飄浮海面 身份待查","createTime":"2018-09-18T05:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T09:29:12.000Z","uid":121079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f410183e55052535dbdf72027a901fec7ba293b3","tid":826182,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"其實西貢的災情都幾嚴重,  海灣燒烤場完全冇曬, 好多船沉咗或者擱淺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/130730_68bc23537afbffde801d1b9bc110c6b3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F130730_68bc23537afbffde801d1b9bc110c6b3.JPG&h=dddc9cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/131338_70276a2b438b9f0ad83d61718f3b7fdd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F131338_70276a2b438b9f0ad83d61718f3b7fdd.JPG&h=371e194e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/131612_f6987642b43c9f3992982d03170dbdb6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F131612_f6987642b43c9f3992982d03170dbdb6.JPG&h=17b24399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/131718_310b0ce78b28662e90f9b2879d495f2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F131718_310b0ce78b28662e90f9b2879d495f2c.jpg&h=28c84434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58694071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694071&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5837f291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694071&h=ce9e74eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58694071</a><br />\n<br />\n【山竹災後】西貢發現男屍飄浮海面 身份待查<br />\n<br />\n西貢海傍街7號對開碼頭，早上8時23分，途人發現一名男性浮屍，在西貢魚類批發市場對開海面飄浮，由於受「山竹」吹襲影響，海面佈滿垃圾，當時男浮屍在垃圾堆中飄浮，屍身明顯發脹瘀黑。救援人員用橡皮艇將浮屍撈起上岸，警方大為緊張，正調查死者身份，暫未知死者是否因「山竹」吹襲的傷亡者。據了解，死者年約50歲。<br />\n據現場所見，西貢海傍一帶滿目瘡痍，不少船都已在風暴中破損及被吹上岸，令人關注死者會否有可能是船主又或是漁民。有西貢居民則表示，區內只得小型的避風塘，欠缺有足夠泊位的大型避風塘，故打風時不少漁船或遊艇都沒有安全泊位可使用（見另稿）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58694384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694384&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d275e2a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694384&h=fd8461a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180918/58694384</a><br />\n<br />\n【山竹災後】西貢海舖滿垃圾 逾千萬遊艇衝上岸<br />\n<br />\n強颱風「山竹」破壞力驚人，屬低窪地區的西貢、白沙灣、相思灣一帶首當其衝，它襲港時，西貢海傍區域其實是重災區，不時受到數米高的大浪拍擊，10號風球當日早上，西貢更曾錄得最高陣風達到每小時181公里，海水出現倒灌，並出現一個個漩渦；西貢碼頭附近對開海面，風高浪急，停泊的船隻、遊艇被吹得七零八落，部份更衝上岸，損壞不堪。<br />\n山竹災後，碼頭對開海面全舖滿垃圾，驟眼看已不是海，而是垃圾江，小艇浸在垃圾堆中，不忍卒睹，有遊艇衝上石灘擱淺，災情嚴重。部分遭到破壞及沖上岸的，包括價值以千萬元計的遊艇，亦有遊艇或漁船傾側入水，漁民及船主均損失慘重，岸邊的情況可說是滿目瘡痍，仿如遭受海嘯侵襲，令人想起災難片《明日之後》。<br />\n在漁民及水上人的fb群組中，不少人都抱怨政府近兩天都未有深入跟進西貢的災情。不少居民都認為，造成嚴重災情的主因，是西貢區內一直未有興建具抗風浪能力的合格大型避風塘（只得小型避風塘），亦未有足夠石堤保護西頁碼頭一帶，結果在山竹襲港時不少船隻都無地方避巨浪，最終損毀，甚感無奈。不少紛留言指對西貢災情感到「好心痛」、「喊咗出來」。有居民促請政府盡快在西貢區興建大型避風塘，也希望拖拉多年的「在西貢碼頭對開及西沙興建兩條石堤」的計劃，不會再因為有人不滿影響「靚景」而反對。<br />\n留言的市民中，原本不少人都指唯一慶幸是「西貢暫未有人傷亡」，未料今晨即發現西貢區出現浮屍，居民關注死者會否有可能是山竹襲港時的受害人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T-m8VGvEuxk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT-m8VGvEuxk&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=92658b96\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T-m8VGvEuxk</a>"},{"pid":"794f632fe7cead18c4ca67f0ec3b8a4485b662c1","tid":826182,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdc48d1adf29e527e74aeda42573af1af01c5d5","tid":826182,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"趕返工？"},{"pid":"e300c08de2c074203d55fe3cd26dc762dcc06892","tid":826182,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a57e5f9c66afad06a16df83fa52bbc57807c7881","tid":826182,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭又可以繼續用安然度過形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68546b315bb6530f6175844d16efde35bfc70cff","tid":826182,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e300c08de2c074203d55fe3cd26dc762dcc06892","tid":826182,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:23:50.000Z","msg":"西貢group有人話好似係鬼佬"},{"pid":"76ea27e75ec226890c2ff4dd8cab8d217867fcbb","tid":826182,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"跳海自殺啦擺明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24695b901030e87a6bf1ff619a1351548fda0a00","tid":826182,"uid":121079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"76ea27e75ec226890c2ff4dd8cab8d217867fcbb","tid":826182,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"跳海自殺啦擺明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"可能是山竹襲港時的受害人"},{"pid":"73f07d9999aa95dacb4aea01e8a95440466f1b3f","tid":826182,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ea27e75ec226890c2ff4dd8cab8d217867fcbb","tid":826182,"uid":36178,"like":0,"disl