/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"可能係同沈船有關，西貢避風塘唔夠位，有啲船會泊去早禾坑對開，船主就留守係船上，上面藍色嗰隻大船，聽聞4千幾萬，都係泊係早禾坑。<br />\n<br />\n今次竹係西貢起碼沈咗或者擱淺咗十幾廿隻船，沿海邊災情都幾嚴重，海濱長廊啲石牆操爛晒，只係因為尋日啲路Block哂，記者仲係入唔到西貢，新聞冇報。"},{"pid":"397598c3025bb754b9c72ba3ef7574360cc30d29","tid":826182,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e533bdcbda1ee8fc1d40de85d6b5d8a9e93e33d","tid":826182,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/bkn-20180918121502038-0918_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fbkn-20180918121502038-0918_00822_001.html&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=852bb1a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/bkn-20180918121502038-0918_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1c5c31291d9f0a7b28650d0f7e09ad841962723","tid":826182,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"生果報半碼版:[img]<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537235626_e7e2.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537235626_e7e2.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=93351da2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537235626_e7e2.jpg[img]</a>"},{"pid":"5b880818455560599db1189c83b318b15c72347c","tid":826182,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"做乜屍體既相又唔post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}